headline: Quanta (PWR) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of infrastructure solutions provider Quanta (NYSE:PWR) jumped 4% in the afternoon session after an analyst at Truist Securities raised the price target on the stock from $472 to $521. The analyst, Jamie Cook, maintained a "Buy" rating on Quanta Services. This adjustment represented a 10.38% increase in the price target and indicated a positive outlook for the company.
